title: #171: Lights Off (@BillyWayneDavis)
itunes:title: Lights Off with Billy Waynes Davis
description: Billy Wayne Davis had me over to his dinge hole of a motel 2 years ago to talk to me about his imploded marriage. It was a wreck and he's finally out of it. I held on to this one for so long because much like a beaten dog, Billy Wayne was still scared of his ex until now. The introduction was recorded on top of the Great Wall of China.
